Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:10.85,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}字幕搬運：大風鈴               來自極影字幕組、bilibili
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:10.85,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}業餘謄抄，僅供交流學習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:01:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,交往……我也不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我考慮一下……再回覆你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之後跟安曇君……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上就沒說過話了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,新幹線  yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真亢奮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲帶了嗎  小太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,從今天起我要告別平角底褲改穿三角褲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等著看我的三角褲出道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？才換？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都穿的三角褲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？  我的出道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:48.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,なんとなく頭の中で君が  離れなくなっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:48.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不知為何  你的身影一直縈繞在我的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:09.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,途切れの会話だね いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:09.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我們倆的對話總是斷斷續續呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:16.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,息も吐き出せないほどのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:16.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,和你交談時  我總覺得呼吸困難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:20.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,目が合った瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:20.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,在眼神交會的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:29.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,また何かが胸を貫いてゆく  今!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:29.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我感覺彷彿有什麼擊中了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:37.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,大好きな人がイマココに居る、居るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:37.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,現在我最喜歡的人就在我眼前  在我眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:44.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,最高の毎日は恋の晴れパレーパレード
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:44.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,每天都幸福得像戀愛大遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:50.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,近づきたい 誰よりも君に今、いま以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:50.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想靠近你  我想靠得比誰都近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:03:01.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,会いたくて会いに行く  笑顔また見つけに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:03:01.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想見你  我現在就去尋找你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來檢查全員的隨身物品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老師  那是女孩子的……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就由我來確認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不准帶手機的吧  先交給我保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,暴露啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,日高老師好騙多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好  下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,陣亡了一票啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你把手機藏哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我藏內衣裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙手機在內褲裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好屌  內褲耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的  黃爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,外面根本看不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我先打開了  再用膠帶封上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好  這樣一來有回覆也能收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜親  鏡頭右邊點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,往上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說是促成戀愛的神明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.73,Notes',,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1032,940)}戀愛占卜簽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  半吉究竟是好是壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,財運盡緣分也盡  這都是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,發給永原  發給永原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  小茜親大吉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.40,Notes'',,0,0,0,,{\frz233.3\pos(1086,486.999)}戀愛  曖昧的態度乃災禍之源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一起選給社團帶的禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一二……八人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,手帕如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有點微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,鑰匙扣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,男生就得送吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,翹毛君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,選一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,問我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,男生喜歡哪種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大的好些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我在選給社團帶的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  男生很能吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡吃什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,問我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  參考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是男生也喜歡甜食的……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,請於十分鐘之內進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等會有安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室好小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我沖下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這誰的內褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,寫名字沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋  好像胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  別看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-連擊  -不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,連擊  連擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等……喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,四連擊  四連擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真心厲害啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要來彈幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好多彈幕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了吧  我這算贏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,輸了輸了  你厲害  算我輸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的假的  -行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個到誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,意中人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有……意中人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,誰啊誰啊誰啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,比良？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,被告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比良蠻好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,交往唄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？說得容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好懸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真心嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你們來幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,別害我們被老師罵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  真無情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不歡迎你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼的嘛  難得出來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.5\pos(1000,590)\fs45}現在在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不暴露就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來了來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好  二連  四連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,八連八連八連  來了來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1228.999,627)\fs40}現在在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(790,723)\fs40}聊戀愛之類的話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是吧  -OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,砍啊砍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋
